Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 有人来商谈动画化的事情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:08.87,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be3\blur3}翻译 妹控　小乱　小雨　印第安马 校译 印第安马 后期 DK 压制 童话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.96,0:00:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就商谈的话 还是稍微早了点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人也说了只是先打个招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.39,0:00:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要对亚豆说起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让她期望过高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 还是可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」的人气这么高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.09,0:00:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要画出有趣的漫画就一定能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直是抱着这种想法在创作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有一天能动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:49.21,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}梦想 梦想 梦想 梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:56.51,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}每次实现时 才会崩坏的 梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:01:00.97,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}为何 即便如此 我仍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:07.77,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}不断寻求 继续奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:09.89,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}久别重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:11.35,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}「气氛改变了？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:14.52,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}岁月流逝了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:19.26,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}「还是那个时候快乐」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:24.25,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}失去的 许多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.79,0:01:31.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}其实 早就觉察到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:40.42,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}继续呐喊吧 继续挣扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:46.77,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}不要再 用谁来作为借口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:53.19,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}还有想要传达的话 很多 很多 很多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:57.61,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}梦想的前路 只剩下梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:04.14,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,480)}温泉与二选一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看啊 最高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天过来的 加藤小姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北见莉莉香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是个出道的声优
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还是个学生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你在调查这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是有公司想让「REVERSI」动画化嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有点按耐不住心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在就这样怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是确定了能够动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算动画化也是以后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在最重要的是让我们的漫画的变得更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高 这次的正月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我们第一次有空休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这月30号到下月3号准备休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说 但也没啥事可干
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计到最后还是在家工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我计划和香耶去蜜月后的第一次旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜月之后？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在鬼怒川3日2晚旅行之后就没出去过？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香耶 她也太可怜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想时隔4年半后再故地重游一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香耶也叫你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为 为什么啊  你们两个去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是当电灯泡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无论何时都在一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是这时候你不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会感觉怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像公司旅行那样 去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 极乐 极乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很像老头子 但也想不出别的形容词了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没有打扰你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要问多少遍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们3人在一起才更加开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然像这样悠闲的休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才最爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为平时都那么拼命努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才格外能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果经常来的话 就感受不到这种感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来就到吃饭时间啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丰盛的料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们太慢了 所以我先喝起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 香耶 没在耍酒疯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人 今年也请多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城 一直以来也非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家秋人多谢你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不怎么能喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝  我喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好饱 好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 惯例的乒乓球大会 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 吃了一肚子 马上就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！ 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打 我打
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香耶 打太猛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱爆了 你们两个大男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我用左手打
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 小瞧我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动之后 酒劲上头了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城 不要睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}今年终于要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起看新年日出的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 要开始倒计时了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 「REVERSI」的话 一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给亚豆发新年祝福短信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又是一两句
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩不这样的话就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 天开始亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望今年也一帆风顺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」的人气越来越高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城什么愿望都不许吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年第一天的日出需要许愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是应该初次参拜神社的时候许愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都会许愿的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能和香耶还有秋人的关系一直这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城君~你如果不是美保的男朋友的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也对真城君…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真城君能来太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 这样很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人 香耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么开心的新年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次还要一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次美保也要一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高 醒着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 香耶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也正准备睡觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我要不就在这边睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太恶心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初三的暑假我们不是每天都睡在同一屋檐下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初三的暑假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又感觉是最近才发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时开始我们一步不停地走到今天真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9年半的时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是转瞬间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然也有艰难的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的运气还是很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「骄傲」「努力」「运气」中的运气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得能和秋人相遇是我最大的运气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你没有对我说「一起画漫画吧」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道现在的自己在做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是找到其他的目标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该不会有「成为日本第一的漫画家」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「和亚豆结婚什么的」这样巨大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个梦想也快要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经近得仿佛伸手可及
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」的话 一定可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以说些自负的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途中的丑事不当回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是多恶心的话随便说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得漫画和人生是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周刊漫画就是一周
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生就是到死的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被赋予的时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟能创造出多么美好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说绝对不能偷工减料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骄傲和运气固然重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最重要的是努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不自负嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得就是你说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还有「体力」和「精神」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后就是「毅力」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去之后就要开始工作啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到能这么快交稿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们想留充裕的时间来创作出更好的原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4号发表的第2卷已经再版了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上第1卷已经达到50万本了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过 「ZOMBIE☆GUN」也再版了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 第2卷还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是「REVERSI」卖的更好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来发展顺利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能追上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！就这样迎头赶上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然两部都很有人气 但是也才连载半年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这个夏天「CROW」的动画会完结
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按现状来看 也只能在这两部作品中选择一部了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到观众群体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得同一作者的「ZOMBIE☆GUN」比较顺理成章
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是按「ZOMBIE☆GUN」的展开来看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画剧情很快就会追上原作的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这点来看 「REVERSI」每一话的内容都很紧凑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:10:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没那么容易追上原作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那种剧情对小孩子来说过于复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想扩大观众群的话 还是应该选择我说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那种情况让制作方调整一下就可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相田你相当推崇「REVERSI」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二郎也说过还不想动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就是「REVERSI」了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他知道有动画化的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但估计觉得一切还为时尚早所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就去问问服部的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他说OK的话 就决定选择「REVERSI」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是要问问他有没有意向秋天开始动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则说什么都是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要重新问一下雄二郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」动画化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有决定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编辑长想知道你有没有意向从秋天开始动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在「CROW」之后呢 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以理解为你想做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我稍微考虑一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有任何问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…「CROW」的动画做了几年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到7年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起长期连载
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更想创作出能让大家接受的作品！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照亚城木君的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好在动画开播前漫画就已经完结了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何最好在动画播放期间继续连载漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是亚城木君很固执啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果找不到可以接受的办法 是无法继续的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 一脸严肃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 虽然很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不能简单地答复你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说这是为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常的反应应该是「动画化！太棒了！」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之 请让我考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之尽快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…算是问一下你的意愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」就暂时不动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就算为了更好地动画化 也还是尽量往后延比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得要连载3年以上之后才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接「CROW」档的动画片估计…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟亚城木君说 他们肯定是希望动画化的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从画漫画开始这就是他们的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么如果告诉他们动画化的条件是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画播放期间一直保持连载…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果这样导致漫画变得无趣的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把动画开始前漫画也许会完结的事情如实反应给上边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但这样的话可能就失去动画化的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想太多 在动画化之前保持沉默就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样就太不负责任了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我一个人想破脑袋也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别着急哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还没有定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上边问我有没有意向让「REVERSI」接秋番
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下 都说了还没定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是问我有没有意向而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能拒绝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们同意 事情就定下来了是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做 一定要做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 事情还没到你们想的那个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}太棒啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}动画化！ 动画化！ 动画化！……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 你们先冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 在动画完结前要保持连载？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是黑恶魔和白恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修巴鲁兹和拜森的对决结束后我们三人也要一起考虑后续
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方提出在动画结束前漫画不可以完结的条件了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 上边虽然没有这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是站在动画制作公司的立场上考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方肯定希望连载能持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天开始的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照现在的构思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修巴鲁兹和拜森的对决在秋天就会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在动画播放过程中漫画绝对不能完结吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 并不是绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果把动画开始时漫画会完结的计划报告上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画化的计划也许就会被取消
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不说实情直接动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也于心不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 至少在动画完结前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 哪怕你们能连载至动画开播一年后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来讲也会轻松不少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高 我们不能放弃这次动画化的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在动画开播满一年之前 我不会让原作完结的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样你能保证作品的质量不会下降吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」高无疑问会成为杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望拖长剧情让作品的质量下降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事不是之前才决定的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你想要动画化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到秋天时 连载就满一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于动画来讲 也有了相当充足的原作资源
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就暂时放弃动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到作品完结
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候制作方还有动画化的打算的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再考虑动画化的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 好不容易有这个机会 要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拒绝这个机会我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高 我可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我努力去完成原作就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是 勉强连载即便降低质量也无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不会让质量下降的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 不像你们的风格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 虽然我提出让你们尽量延长连载
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很想动画化 但是绝对不能因此降低作品质量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你们一定会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木是为了我 为了我个人的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学的时候 在开始画漫画之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和现在正从事声优工作的亚豆美保约定过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的作品动画化 女主角由她来担任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现了这个梦想 我们就结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想实现前不会左顾右盼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不约会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不见面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你可能会认为我们很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木邀我和他一起成为漫画家的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然产生了这个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我下定决心要做一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木是想让我实现这个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你们这么拘泥于动画化的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我反对为了我个人的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了动画化不惜降低作品质量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像服部先生说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等连载结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候还有动画化的邀请也为时不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么哪 不会降低质量的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在接到邀请了 只要接受就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管用什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管用什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是作品质量下降吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚豆也不希望看到这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请来了 只要坦率接受就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为亚城木梦叶想做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 连载就按你们的想法去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时完结都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人追究 责任由我来承担
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多美好的梦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的作品动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主角由亚豆美保来演绎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能实现这个梦想就结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能从中学坚持到现在这点也非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是为了实现这个梦想 也要同意动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我支持你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太世故了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定已经丢失了这种纯粹的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上头问我想不想动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要回答想 不管怎样都想就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 刚才服部先生来过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你们两个干吗都闷不吭声的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因为香耶来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是因为香耶太可爱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个哪根筋不对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 亚城木君他们也有意思做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 请务必推荐「REVERSI」动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是新妻君为动画化所画的「ZOMBIE☆GUN」的原创NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共20话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画用原创NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不是说动画化还太早了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽然我是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 作为亚城木粉丝的新妻君的话应该感到高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果单行本的销量被超过了就高兴不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果动画化就有可能被超越了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 也不能阻止「REVERSI」动画化…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说「ZOMBIE☆GUN」想动画化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了很多次了吗 很快就会追上原作不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就画足够动画用的原创故事就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得「ZOMBIE☆GUN」动画化为时尚早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我自认为动画很快会追上原作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是新妻君 就能像这样不断画出动画用NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以动画用的角度来处理画面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」会动画化的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了成为真正的第一位的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚城木君也说想从秋天开始动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他们说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是头大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没让你们去问作家的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来也以为「ZOMBIE☆GUN」会拒绝动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该更加慎重地确认过才对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下难办了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新妻君和亚城木君都干劲十足的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边都希望秋天开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这次不行 动画化也是迟早的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」必须在这次动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在被「REVERSI」抢走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是问卷排名还是单行本销量说不定都会被超过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪部作品能成为真正的招牌的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分水岭！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的招牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天会决定选择哪部作品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我都说了那么多遍还没确定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新妻画动画用的NAME的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」显然更强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是接「CROW」的档 所以可能性很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然决定权在编辑长手上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最好还是别抱太大希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 昨天服部先生来过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 来过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你俩为什么都这么垂头丧气的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊 明明有香耶在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 超可爱的香耶都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个…到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 服部先生 欢迎…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.34,0:22:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这件事还是亲口跟你们说比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事…你是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是动画化的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:23:08.70,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}为何…总是如此 每次在梦中接近你都是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:17.11,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}面向前方 紧紧抓住 这样 一点一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:25.45,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}相互支持着朝着约定的地方前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:32.88,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}缺乏自信的时候 将手放在胸前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:41.83,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}重读我们共同书写的篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:48.99,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}从过去到未来 一直持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:24:05.09,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)\fad(0,1000)}直到宝贵的梦想实现的那天 永远保持真实的自己
